                                                                                   🔥 BEFORE LEARNING SYSTEM DESIGN  🔥

* GATHERING THE REQUIRMENT :  requirement comes through various sources.
                     1. Customers,
                     2. Product Managers,
                     3. Self Driven ideas.

* IDENTIFY FOR CATEGORITION OF THE REQUIREMENT : there are two categories
                     1. Functional Requirement => exact kon sa feature ko build krne ki jarurt hai jise user aa ke use kr ske.(what should the system do) jaise:
                                                                                                                                                      - users can signup & login
                                                                                                                                                      - users can buy a subscription
                                                                                                                                                      - user can play & pause the video.
                     2. Non-Functional Requirment => hmara system kis tarike se perform krega,uske ander kya kya qualities hogi(performance,scalibility),jaise:
                                                                                                                                                      - secure system with authentication / autherization 
                                                                                                                                                      - low latency for video ( video play hone me jyda time n lge).
                                                                                                                                                      - scalable system ( millions of user watch kr paye).
                     

* Application Development Process (SDLC): are we going to build it in a day ?
                   No, actually there is various steps to do which will take lots of time.
                     1. Design,
                     2. Developement,
                     3. Testing,
                     4. Deployement.

* SCOPING : decide karna ki system me kya include hoga aur kya nahi.
            ex- Kaunse features build honge,
                Kaunse nahi (out of scope),
                System ka size kya hai,
                Complexity kitni hai.


* MVP = Minimum Viable Product :  Product ka sabse basic version jo real users use kar saken.
                              isme POC = Proof of Concept hota hai -> Ye idea technically possible hai ya nahi? jisme technology test krna,Feasibility check karna
                              jiske bad inverstor ko pich kr skte hai invest ke liye.



* Core Components of Any Application :
                              1. Compute (Processing Power) : Ye wo part hai jo logic execute karta hai.
                                                              Examples:
                                                                       Backend server (Spring Boot app – jo tum bana rahe ho)
                                                                       APIs run hona
                                                                       Business logic execute hona
                              2. Storage (Data Store)  : Yaha data store hota hai
                                                              Examples:
                                                                       Database (MySQL, PostgreSQL)
                                                                       Cache (Redis)
                                                                       File storage (images, videos)
                              3. Network (Communication) : Sabko connect karta hai.
                                                              Examples:
                                                                       Internet / HTTP calls 
                                                                       APIs communication (Frontend → Backend call, Backend → Database connection)
                                                                       Microservices communication.


🔷 What is System Design ?
System Design = ek application ko kaise design karenge (architecture level pe).
System Design Pattern ek proven architectural solution hota hai jo large-scale software systems ki common problems solve karta hai
jaise:
 - scalability
 - maintainability
 - availability
 - fault tolerance
 - performance


